{"tid":1630564,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"禁蒙面法目的係將黑警拉既人全部必定入罪","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:06.000Z","uid":131696,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c15aafda3c1cf99ca0db2963b581aa23aeefc60c","tid":1630564,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"被拉既人九成都戴口罩 亦都係集會範圍附近<br />\n非法集會既必告到 但禁蒙面法門檻低到仆街 好易入<br />\n之後就唔存在所謂既警察濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2312fa606f37f34d597e325bc3a414417218733","tid":1630564,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:55:06.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c424ad5567e7aac2cc512844e9074d73bbc2542","tid":1630564,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d30049f251ecdb8a9c77fd517b58d860aecfb47","tid":1630564,"uid":211525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"唔舒服帶口罩行街經過有咩問題"},{"pid":"5c578b20b886e8f4ec54720871ad4294f4a939bc","tid":1630564,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"[長文][召喚全世界] 嘈完就入黎 睇下下一步應該做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ead6e993165bf447bfe80429634bac6c014d570","tid":1630564,"uid":129783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c15aafda3c1cf99ca0db2963b581aa23aeefc60c","tid":1630564,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"被拉既人九成都戴口罩 亦都係集會範圍附近<br />\n非法集會既必告到 但禁蒙面法門檻低到仆街 好易入<br />\n之後就唔存在所謂既警察濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"告唔入非法集結就唔會告得入蒙面<br />\n因為你唔係一個集結其中一員"},{"pid":"d3ed392293449a5b0ff9c4b6389c3eb6facc9090","tid":1630564,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ead6e993165bf447bfe80429634bac6c014d570","tid":1630564,"uid":129783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c15aafda3c1cf99ca0db2963b581aa23aeefc60c","tid":1630564,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"被拉既人九成都戴口罩 亦都係集會範圍附近<br />\n非法集會既必告到 但禁蒙面法門檻低到仆街 好易入<br />\n之後就唔存在所謂既警察濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"告唔入非法集結就唔會告得入蒙面<br />\n因為你唔係一個集結其中一員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"a171c704e22e998b07fb26b7064f6dfc53808143","tid":1630564,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ead6e993165bf447bfe80429634bac6c014d570","tid":1630564,"uid":129783,"lik